description: Family meal times have never been easier with a delicious Chinese-inspired stir-fry, made with just four ingredients!
keywords: Stir-fry,Low saturated fat,Low salt,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Beef,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Dinner Made Easy,Low fat,Peanut free
name: Easy Hoisin Beef StirFry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 Five Tastes stir fry shots Chinese hoisin & garlic

recipeInstructions.text: Soak noodles in a bowl of boiling water for 23 minutes, then drain and set aside.
Heat a large frying pan or wok over high heat. Add the beef and cook for 5 minutes, tossing occasionally, until browned.
Add the vegetables and cook for 34 minutes or until tender. Add the stir-fry shot and stir to combine, about 1 minute.
Add the noodles and cook for 12 minutes, tossing to combine. Divide among bowls to serve.
